For sale: $308,900. The Hennepin plan by LGI Homes offers abundant space and everything you want in a new home. This thoughtfully designed split-level home features an open entertaining space with a chef-ready kitchen, dining room and expansive family room. A full suite of Whirlpool brand appliances, granite countertops, a walk-in pantry and breakfast island are sure to make the kitchen a popular gathering place. Also located on the main level, the private owner's retreat showcases a spacious bedroom, gorgeous bathroom and a large walk-in closet. Downstairs, find two additional bedrooms, each featuring a walk-in closet, plus and a second full bathroom. This home also offers over 600 square feet of unfinished space for future buildout.

For sale: $309,900. The Victoria by LGI Homes delivers a luxurious amount of space in all the right places. This 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom home features a downstairs master retreat with a large walk-in closet and gorgeous en suite bathroom. A spacious family room is adjacent to the dining room and chef-ready kitchen equipped with a full suite of Whirlpool appliances and upgraded cabinets. Additionally, a flex room that can be used as a home office, playroom or fifth bedroom is located on the main level of the home.

For sale: $290,900. The Pepin by LGI Homes at Willow Creek is a beautiful two-story home featuring three bedrooms, two and a half bathrooms and an expansive, open area for entertaining. Move-in ready and equipped with over $10,000 in upgrades, this new home features soaring 9-foot ceilings, eye-catching archways and abundant storage space. The private owner's retreat boasts a beautiful bathroom with a soaking tub, separate shower and enclosed lavatory, in addition to a large walk-in closet. Two secondary bedrooms each include walk-in closets and offer plenty of space for children, guests, a home office or hobby room. The Pepin may also be built with an unfinished lookout basement, fully wired and plumbed for future buildout.

For sale: $275,900. The Hartley plan by LGI Homes at Willow Creek features a functional three-bedroom, two-bathroom layout with a spacious family room. The chef-ready kitchen comes equipped with a full suite of kitchen appliances, upgraded cabinets and a breakfast bar overlooking the family room. The owner's retreat includes an en suite bathroom showcasing a soaking tub and separate, step-in shower. The two secondary bedrooms and full bathroom are sizeable. The Hartley may also be built with an unfinished basement.

Light grays & soft whites are the backdrop, with custom decor pieces in the perfect haze of worn-away whitewashing & other distressed finishes. Transform this area into a hobby farm, dream workshop, man cave, or retreat area. A heavenly setting & updated luxuries make this country estate a rare find!
